                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On December 21, 1951, the Department sent to all diplomatic, <gloss
                        target="#t_TCA1">TCA</gloss>, and <gloss target="#t_ECA1">ECA</gloss>
                    missions in the Far East and South Asia a circular airgram on the subject
                    “Relationship With Japan and Production of Essential Materials.” For text, see
                        <ref target="#pg_126">page 126</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
